      "content": "it's just so exhausting. like, every day is just another day of pretending to care about things that don't even matter on a cosmic scale. if there's no actual point to the noise, then why is it considered \"wrong\" to just want out? wouldn't it be more logical to just choose peace instead of waiting for the universe to force it on us?",
